1042
01:17:01,100 --> 01:17:04,400
Well, some part of me just knew.

1043
01:17:04,900 --> 01:17:06,200
The Gusteau part?

1044
01:17:07,700 --> 01:17:12,300
- Where do you get your inspiration?
