1045
01:17:12,500 --> 01:17:15,100
- Mine is named Colette.
- What?

1046
01:17:16,700 --> 01:17:18,800
Something's stuck in my teeth.

1047
01:17:22,300 --> 01:17:23,600
Health Inspector.

1048
01:17:23,700 --> 01:17:26,300
