Bonjour, ma chérie.
Join us.

1060
01:17:56,100 --> 01:17:58,200
We were just talking
about my inspiration.

1061
01:17:58,400 --> 01:18:00,700
Yes, he calls it his tiny chef.

1062
01:18:02,000 --> 01:18:04,400
Not that, dearest. I meant you.

1063
01:18:07,000 --> 01:18:08,700
- It's him.
- Ego?

1064
01:18:08,800 --> 01:18:09,800
Anton Ego!

1065
01:18:10,000 --> 01:18:11,300
Is that Ego?

1066
01:18:12,000 --> 01:18:13,500
I can't believe it.

1067
01:18:13,600 --> 01:18:16,900
- You are Monsieur Linguini?
- Hello.

1068
01:18:17,000 --> 01:18:21,500
Pardon me for interrupting
your premature celebration,

1069
01:18:21,600 --> 01:18:25,300
but I thought it only fair
to give you a sporting chance

1070
01:18:25,400 --> 01:18:27,600
