against the rules.

1074
01:18:38,700 --> 01:18:40,800
You're Anton Ego.

1075
01:18:42,400 --> 01:18:45,300
You're slow
for someone in the fast lane.

1076
01:18:46,900 --> 01:18:49,900
And you're thin
for someone who likes food.

1077
01:18:53,500 --> 01:18:57,500
I don't like food. I love it.

1078
01:18:57,900 --> 01:19:02,200
If I don't love it, I don't swallow.

1079
01:19:03,500 --> 01:19:07,500
I will return tomorrow night
