1108
01:20:33,300 --> 01:20:34,800
Little Chef?

1109
01:20:44,300 --> 01:20:49,100
This is great, Son.
An inside job. I see the appeal.

1110
01:21:08,700 --> 01:21:09,800
Oof!

1111
01:21:26,000 --> 01:21:27,400
Little Chef?

1112
01:21:28,200 --> 01:21:29,400
Little Chef?

1113
01:21:30,200 --> 01:21:31,800
Hey, Little Chef.

1114
01:21:32,100 --> 01:21:35,200
I thought you went back
to the apartment.

1115
01:21:35,400 --> 01:21:39,500
Then when you weren't there,
I don't know...

1116
01:21:39,900 --> 01:21:43,900
It didn't seem right to leave things
the way that we did, so...

1117
01:21:44,900 --> 01:21:46,800
Look, I don't want to fight.

1118
01:21:47,000 --> 01:21:49,700
I've been under a lot of, you know,
pressure.

1119
01:21:49,900 --> 01:21:53,200
A lot has changed
in not very much time, you know?

1120
01:21:53,300 --> 01:21:54,600
